snippet.title: Jen Saves Ben - Sample
snippet.description: Powerhouse produced video games in custom arcade cabinets for Kevin Smith. The most notable of these custom games is Jen Saves Ben made for Ben Affleck and Jennifer Lopez as a wrap party gift for the film Jersey Girl, as well as one for Smith's comic shop, The Secret Stash.
